// MiniGameSession Endpoints

### Get All Mini-Game Sessions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/mini-game-sessions

### Get Mini-Game Session by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/mini-game-sessions/1

### Get Mini-Game Session by ID (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/mini-game-sessions/99999

### Get Mini-Game Session by ID (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/mini-game-sessions/invalid

### Get Player's Mini-Game Sessions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/mini-game-sessions

### Get Player's Mini-Game Sessions (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/mini-game-sessions

### Get Mini-Game Sessions by Type (Coin Flip)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/mini-game-sessions/type/Coin%20Flip

### Get Mini-Game Sessions by Type (Dice Roll)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/mini-game-sessions/type/Dice%20Roll

### Get Mini-Game Sessions by Type (Slots)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/mini-game-sessions/type/Slots

### Create Mini-Game Session (win)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/mini-game-sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "playerId": 1,
    "gameType": "Coin Flip",
    "result": "win",
    "coinPayout": 100
}

### Create Mini-Game Session (loss)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/mini-game-sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "playerId": 1,
    "gameType": "Coin Flip",
    "result": "loss",
    "coinPayout": 0
}

### Create Mini-Game Session (jackpot)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/mini-game-sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "playerId": 2,
    "gameType": "Slots",
    "result": "jackpot",
    "coinPayout": 5000
}

### Create Mini-Game Session (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/mini-game-sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "playerId": 1
}

### Create Mini-Game Session (negative payout)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/mini-game-sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "playerId": 1,
    "gameType": "Coin Flip",
    "result": "win",
    "coinPayout": -100
}

### Delete Mini-Game Session
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/mini-game-sessions/1

### Delete Mini-Game Session (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/mini-game-sessions/99999

### Get Player's Mini-Game Stats
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/mini-game-stats

### Get Player's Mini-Game Stats (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/mini-game-stats
